<br>
Next question.  Should I use Katakana? or Hiragana?  The little reading I've done so far <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START 8o --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/nerd.gif ALT="8o"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   tells me that if it's an english word use Katanana, if not use Hirgana.  Since it's an english name that's been translated, do you put it in Katakana? or is Katakana not used that much? <br>
